description:
Part 1 of a 'Guitar Conversation' I filmed in Nashville a couple of year ago with the wonderful fingerstyle guitarist Bill Piburn. Bill's a good friend and I always enjoy hearing him play. We had good chat in this conversation and Bill shared some of his guitar secrets with us. You can watch the full Guitar Conversation with Bill, and many other videos in my Guitar Conversations Series by joining me on my Patreon site http://bit.ly/MTML-patreon
